<p class=3D"MsoListParagraph"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#0070C0=
">Structural Assessment and draft scope of works document =E2=80=93<span cl=
ass=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><u>Completed by Friday August 15=
</u>.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoListParagraph"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#0070C0=
">Final scope of works shared with customer for sign-off =E2=80=93<span cla=
